Distribution.
Petropedetes palmipes
occurs mainly in lowland areas (
Fig. 4
). It has been found in southern Cameroon (
Perret 1966
), in Equatorial Guinea (de la
Riva 1994
;
Lasso et al . 2002
) and Gabon (
Lötters et al . 2001
;
Pauwels & Rödel 2007
). The P. p a l m i p e s record from western Cameroon by
Perret & Mertens ( 1957 )
is based on a
P. perreti
specimen (not known at that time).
